<h2>Meeting Cancelled</h2>
<p>Hi <strong>{{inviteeName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>Your meeting <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong> on <strong>{{formatDate startTime}}</strong> has been cancelled.</p>

{{#if cancelReason}}
<p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{cancelReason}}</p>
{{/if}}

<p>You can schedule a new meeting anytime.</p>
